when he got really emotional,

561
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:28,650
and one time it could be considered abuse.

562
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:30,760
Xu Wei.

563
00:35:31,480 --> 00:35:33,400
According to Chinese legal definition,

564
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:37,320
domestic violence occurs between family members

565
00:35:37,640 --> 00:35:40,920
through beating, confinement, binding, abuse,

566
00:35:40,920 --> 00:35:43,920
or other forms against family members

567
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:46,800
causing psychological, physical, sexual

568
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:49,200
harm and devastation.

569
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:51,360
In the US, it's much simpler.

570
00:35:51,360 --> 00:35:53,240
Any physical violence

571
00:35:53,640 --> 00:35:55,200
constitutes domestic abuse.

572
00:35:55,200 --> 00:35:57,600
If David has laid his hands on you even once,

573
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:59,760
that's already domestic violence.

574
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:01,560
Senior.

575
00:36:02,160 --> 00:36:04,290
Do you have some difficult situation?

576
00:36:04,600 --> 00:36:06,360
Do you know what marriage is?

577
00:36:08,240 --> 00:36:09,600
Dating someone

578
00:36:10,520 --> 00:36:11,760
and marrying someone

579
00:36:12,040 --> 00:36:13,680
are completely different things.

580
00:36:13,680 --> 00:36:15,480
When dating, you can do whatever you want,

581
00:36:15,480 --> 00:36:17,280
if you get along well, you're inseparable,

582
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:18,960
if not, you just go your separate ways.

583
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:20,490
But marriage is different,

584
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:22,960
marriage binds two people from completely different backgrounds

585
00:36:22,960 --> 00:36:24,160
together.

586
00:36:24,440 --> 00:36:26,200
It's not just about two people loving each other,

587
00:36:26,200 --> 00:36:29,360
it's more about when facing each other's flaws,

588
00:36:30,360 --> 00:36:32,480
learning to be tolerant of each other.

589
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:34,280
You need to learn to be accepting.

590
00:36:34,280 --> 00:36:36,160
But we're talking about domestic violence now,

591
00:36:36,160 --> 00:36:37,760
domestic violence is not acceptable.

592
00:36:37,760 --> 00:36:39,890
I know David's personality very well,

593
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:42,680
he'll change if he's made a mistake.

594
00:36:42,680 --> 00:36:44,800
The matters between us as husband and wife

595
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:47,530
I don't expect outsiders like you to understand.

596
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:51,600
As for you saying David hit Cui Fengjun,

597
00:36:52,160 --> 00:36:54,290
I believe he's not that kind of person.

598
00:36:56,560 --> 00:36:58,040
I'm happy that you came to have lunch with me today,

599
00:36:58,040 --> 00:36:59,160
I really am.

600
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:00,840
But if it's to make me

601
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:02,970
add false accusations against David,

602
00:37:03,360 --> 00:37:06,290
then there's no need to continue this conversation.

603
00:37:49,520 --> 00:37:50,760
Honey!

604
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:52,240
Where are you going?

605
00:37:52,240 --> 00:37:53,240
None of your business!

606
00:37:53,240 --> 00:37:53,960
Stop this,

607
00:37:54,240 --> 00:37:56,080
you can't keep dwelling on that.

608
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:57,440
It's not your concern!

609
00:37:58,120 --> 00:37:59,840
Honey, I was wrong.

610
00:38:00,160 --> 00:38:01,160
I shouldn't have yelled at you.

611
00:38:01,160 --> 00:38:02,680
I shouldn't have spent money on that camera.

612
00:38:02,680 --> 00:38:03,800
I was too selfish.

613
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:05,080
Please don't be angry, okay?

614
00:38:05,080 --> 00:38:06,480
Don't you understand?

615
00:38:06,840 --> 00:38:08,680
This isn't about the camera.

616
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:11,240
Honey, honey.

617
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:12,800
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

618
00:38:12,800 --> 00:38:14,200
It's all my fault.

619
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:16,690
I'm angry about your selfishness,

620
00:38:16,840 --> 00:38:18,760
you treat that camera like a treasure, but what about me...

621
00:38:18,760 --> 00:38:20,880
I know I was insensitive,

622
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:22,730
I ruined your good intentions.

623
00:38:23,080 --> 00:38:24,200
I know I was wrong,

624
00:38:24,440 --> 00:38:26,570
and I've already returned the camera.

625
00:38:27,000 --> 00:38:28,000
Returned it?

626
00:38:28,120 --> 00:38:29,160
This whole situation

627
00:38:29,160 --> 00:38:31,040
happened because I didn't discuss it with you

628
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:32,880
and bought the camera on my own.

629
00:38:33,560 --> 00:38:34,490
I'm begging you,

630
00:38:35,040 --> 00:38:36,040
please forgive me,

631
00:38:36,040 --> 00:38:37,840
don't be angry anymore, please.

632
00:38:41,400 --> 00:38:42,000
Honey.

633
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:43,360
Sit down, please sit,

634
00:38:43,360 --> 00:38:44,120
come here,

635
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:45,800
please, have a seat.

636
00:38:47,120 --> 00:38:49,560
I'm not trying to make excuses,

637
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:52,490
I've been really anxious these past few days,

638
00:38:52,560 --> 00:38:54,020
my mind is full of worries.

639
00:38:55,520 --> 00:38:56,320
So,

640
00:38:56,680 --> 00:38:57,920
I thought about buying myself

641
00:38:57,920 --> 00:38:59,320
something I really wanted,

642
00:38:59,320 --> 00:39:01,480
to make myself feel a little better.

643
00:39:01,920 --> 00:39:03,980
Is it about the overseas assignment?

644
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:06,760
Yes, the results will be out in a few days.

645
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:08,520
Your company's assignments

646
00:39:08,720 --> 00:39:11,250
are always to far places like Southeast Asia,

647
00:39:11,760 --> 00:39:13,920
we'd barely see each other all year.

648
00:39:18,560 --> 00:39:21,360
But if I really get sent abroad, that would be good,

649
00:39:21,880 --> 00:39:24,720
at least it would secure my status and job.

650
00:39:26,160 --> 00:39:27,880
We need to think long-term.

651
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:29,540
It always comes back to

652
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:31,680
this work visa issue,

653
00:39:31,680 --> 00:39:33,810
having to rely on some lottery system,

654
00:39:34,120 --> 00:39:35,280
it's so unreliable.

655
00:39:35,720 --> 00:39:36,960
Otherwise, with how hard you work,

656
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:38,820
they'd definitely give it to you.

657
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:49,680
You're still thinking about

658
00:39:50,720 --> 00:39:52,320
not winning the lottery draw earlier this year.

659
00:39:52,320 --> 00:39:54,450
I've already settled for second best.

660
00:39:54,680 --> 00:39:55,640
I just hope

661
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:58,400
the company will give me the overseas assignment,

662
00:39:58,400 --> 00:40:00,920
so I can hang in there until April next year

663
00:40:00,920 --> 00:40:02,160
and try my luck again.

664
00:40:04,480 --> 00:40:05,920
You need to stay positive.

665
00:40:05,920 --> 00:40:08,580
The overseas assignment will work out for sure.

666
00:40:13,040 --> 00:40:13,960
Xu Wei.

667
00:40:14,320 --> 00:40:16,440
Any new developments lately?

668
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:20,160
Professor Chen, the first cycle showed good drug efficacy.

669
00:40:20,160 --> 00:40:20,840
However,

670
00:40:20,840 --> 00:40:22,840
after entering the second observation cycle,

671
00:40:22,840 --> 00:40:24,640
we haven't seen any new progress.

672
00:40:24,640 --> 00:40:27,170
This is already a significant breakthrough.

673
00:40:28,160 --> 00:40:29,680
Our previous experiments

674
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:33,400
never even made it past the first cycle.

675
00:40:33,720 --> 00:40:35,780
Once the drug development succeeds,

676
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:38,400
it will benefit patients across Asia.

677
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:41,920
That's the true value of the data, isn't it?

678
00:40:43,240 --> 00:40:45,520
David and I, from day one,

679
00:40:45,520 --> 00:40:47,160
have never been in this for profit.

680
00:40:47,160 --> 00:40:48,600
The final results of our research will definitely

681
00:40:48,600 --> 00:40:50,120
be introduced to the Asian market

682
00:40:50,120 --> 00:40:51,480
to benefit more patients.

683
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:54,360
You're so young yet have such noble aspirations,

684
00:40:54,680 --> 00:40:56,880
willing to give up fame and fortune

685
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:58,280
for the greater good.

686
00:40:59,040 --> 00:41:00,240
I'm very pleased.

687
00:41:01,680 --> 00:41:04,640
Come, breakfast is ready.

688
00:41:14,840 --> 00:41:16,840
Haven't you received the email yet?

689
00:41:18,680 --> 00:41:19,760
Don't worry,

690
00:41:19,920 --> 00:41:22,440
you've worked the most overtime in the company these past six months,

691
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:24,280
and your performance is the best in the entire team.

692
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:27,000
If the company doesn't keep you, who would they keep?

693
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:28,720
There's a bunch of PhDs waiting in line,

694
00:41:28,720 --> 00:41:30,360
and I'm just a master's student.

695
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:31,760
If I don't work this hard,

696
00:41:31,960 --> 00:41:34,040
the company definitely won't keep me.

697
00:41:34,040 --> 00:41:36,080
I should have studied electrical engineering.

698
00:41:36,080 --> 00:41:37,720
Without a work visa now,

699
00:41:37,720 --> 00:41:39,120
I can't submit my application,

700
00:41:39,120 --> 00:41:40,080
and without submitting an application,

701
00:41:40,080 --> 00:41:41,240
nothing can be done.

702
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:44,040
It's not necessarily that absolute.

703
00:41:44,040 --> 00:41:45,960
Having a job is already pretty good.

704
00:41:45,960 --> 00:41:47,920
Even with a job, you wouldn't dare buy a house here.

705
00:41:47,920 --> 00:41:49,560
Back in 2008, my cousin's friend

706
00:41:49,560 --> 00:41:50,720
was working here.

707
00:41:51,160 --> 00:41:52,720
Then he took leave to visit family in China,

708
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:53,980
and just as he arrived,

709
00:41:54,360 --> 00:41:56,760
the company started layoffs and fired him.

710
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:57,880
The problem was

711
00:41:57,880 --> 00:42:00,140
this guy had already bought a house here.

712
00:42:00,280 --> 00:42:01,840
So he did everything possible

713
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:02,800
to come back and sell the house,

714
00:42:02,800 --> 00:42:04,860
and then fled back to China in a panic.

715
00:42:05,200 --> 00:42:06,240
Without a green card,

716
00:42:06,240 --> 00:42:07,480
you just can't live

717
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:09,280
with any real peace of mind here.

718
00:44:00,000 --> 00:44:00,360
[Life Producer-Cra]
